            [
                ""
            ],
            [
                "I fill it out and it says: ‘Hi! my name is: [tn], Hobbies:"
            ],
            [
                "Eating, sleeping, videogames, repeat."
            ],
            [
                "Awesome [tn], and just in time. The event is about to start,"
            ],
            [
                "so let me tell you that if someone gives you their contact information, you can just send a photo to me."
            ],
            [
                "I’ll scan it, and by the end of the event I'll give you a brief on how many potential partners you’ve got."
            ],
            [
                " If you feel nervous, remember that I won’t be far away! And [tn], I advice you to choose well…"
            ],
            [
                "Getting into a relationship isn't something to be taken lightly or to rush into. So take your time getting to know the people here, and even if you don’t find anybody, remember-"
            ],
            [
                "Suddenly, a high-pitched bell announces the beginning of the event. Helpie hurriedly gives me a thumbs up and I signal them to walk back to give me some space."
            ],
            [
                "Soon after, people begin sitting on tables as I wait patiently for someone to approach me. But of course, everybody is just walking past little ‘ol me. "
            ],
            [
                "‘Why did I even come here?’ I think as I get up from my seat."
            ],
            [
                "But out of nowhere, a smack on my table shakes me enough to make my legs sit back down right where I was."
            ],
            [
                "I look up, and a big arm is on top of my table."
            ],
            [
                "Attached to it, a big teethed person is just staring at me,"
            ],
            [
                "completely uninvited as I sit there dumbfounded. "
            ],
            [
                "The smell emanating from this human smells like a mix of sweat and cheap deodorant."
            ],
            [
                "Uhh… may I help yo-"
            ],
            [
                "Shh… I’m exactly what you need baby. My geekcord nametag is Johhney#6769"
            ],
            [
                "Like the car, with two h's"
            ],
            [
                "what’s yours?"
            ],
            [
                "EXCUSE ME?????? WHO THE HELL IS THIS WEIRDO?? "
            ],
            [
                "And like HELL I’m gonna give my nametag just like that."
            ],
            [
                "I my face just shows the most disgusted expression I'm sure I've ever had."
            ],
            [
                "I know baby. You must be surprised to have seen such a mogger among these omegas."
            ],
            [
                "But don't worry… I'll show you what you've been missing your whole life."
            ],
            [
                "This poor excuse of a human then begins puckering up and approaching me slowly."
            ],
            [
                "I looked at Helpie with ‘save me’ eyes"
            ],
            [
                "but to my surprise, Helpie was already on their way to grab “Johhney#6769”."
            ],
            [
                "Helpie drags the idiot away and gets them kicked out of the cafeteria."
            ],
            [
                "What a start."
            ],
            [
                "I exhale after all that ruckus and finally relax."
            ],
            [
                " As soon as I got up to thank Helpie, I hear a bell across the cafeteria."
            ],
            [
                "One of the organizers yells:"
            ],
            [
                "“Every time you hear this bell, that means you have a minute to switch places.”"
            ]
